{"word":"ὑψίκερως","slug":"ὑψίκερως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑψίκερως</b></el> <el>(ὑψί-κερως, ων,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κέρας'><el>κέρας</el></a>\n<p/><i>high-horned</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>: —also metapl. <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <el>ἱψικέρᾱτα πέτραν</el> a <i>high-peaked</i> rock, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b> <a href='S:apud (quoted in)'>ap.</a> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}